                                quả của những cá...</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-4 col-sm-6">
                    <div class="blog__item">
                        <div class="blog__item__pic">
                            <img width="" height=" 240px"
                                src="https://www.reader.com.vn/uploads/news/a_1888617730_sachdetamkhongban4.jpeg"
                                alt="">
                        </div>
                        <div class="blog__item__text">
                            <ul>
                                <li><i class="fa fa-calendar-o"></i> 04/2022</li>
                                <li><i class="fa fa-comment-o"></i> 5</li>
                            </ul>
                            <h5><a
                                    href="https://www.reader.com.vn/review-sach-de-tam-khong-ban-ryunosuke-koike-a647.html">Review
